attributes.body:
Available in Colorado, Massachusetts and New Mexico (Packaging may vary). Visit Joyibles.com/find-joyibles for a store near you!


Take your taste buds on vacation with Tropical Haze Joy Bombs! Every pouch includes an explosive mix of sweet, satisfying flavors: Passion Fruit, Mango, Strawberry Banana, & Piña Colada!


Joy Bombs Candy-Coated Fruit Chews are purposefully dosed to help you dial in or stack the milligrams and effects that you want – but good luck trying to eat just one! With 2.5mg THC in each bite-sized piece, you can micro-dose for days or nom the whole pouch for a 100mg adventure!


Perfect for sharing, Joy Bombs’ signature sugary shell means they'll melt in your mind, but not in your car or pocket. They’re the UNGUMMY you’ve been waiting for!
